{"type": "article", "id": 55823, "title": "奢侈品牌七夕限量款纷纷上线，以及，Uniqlo U 秋冬系列又来了 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-08-01T05:03:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 52302, "name": "madewell"}, {"id": 1653, "name": "Michael Kors"}, {"id": 3322, "name": "Givenchy"}, {"id": 32208, "name": "Montblanc"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180801125312jqzsMa2kYbKXTQuc.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/business-news/markets/ralph-lauren-corp-shares-up-on-q1-earnings-beat-1202767736/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ralph Lauren 第一季度业绩超预期，股票开盘涨幅达 4.2%</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 截至 6 月 30 日的第一季度内，Ralph Lauren 净利润同比增长 83.2% 至 1.09 亿美元。净营收增长 3.2% 至 13.9 以美元。从市场来看，北美本土市场收入下降 2% 至 6.98 亿美元，而欧洲和亚洲市场则分别上涨 8% 和 19%，至 3.51 亿美元和 2.48 亿美元。&nbsp;</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/business-news/financial/salvatore-ferragamo-appoints-micaela-le-divelec-lemmi-new-ceo-1202767758/\" rel=\"nofollow\">上半年净利润与营收双双下跌，Salvatore Ferragamo 任命新任 CEO</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 新任 CEO Micaela Le Divelec Lemmi 此前在 Gucci 有 20 年从业经验，今年 3 月辞去 Gucci 高级副总裁与首席消费官职位。值得一提的是，尽管高层变动频繁，但 Salvatore Ferragamo 的业绩表现仍无起色。周二晚间发布的最新财报显示，今年上半年，该集团净利润同比下跌 23.1% 至 5900 万欧元，营收同比下跌 6.2% 至 6.74 亿欧元。<br></p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/business-news/media/anna-wintour-to-remain-with-vogue-conde-nast-indefinitely-1202768145/\" rel=\"nofollow\">康泰纳仕集团正式否认美国版《Vogue》主编 Anna Wintour 将离职</a></strong> | 康泰纳仕集团 CEO Bob Sauerberg 发表声明称，Anna Wintour 对于集团的未来发展不可或缺。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/madewell-offers-extended-sizing-in-sportswear-and-dresses-1202767892/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Madewell 引入大码尺寸</a></strong> | 从本周二（7 月31 日）起，Madewell 牛仔裤最大尺寸将扩展至 37 码，连衣裙、半身裙、毛衣、上衣和外套等则将提供从 XXS 和 3X 码的全部尺寸。调整后，加大尺寸将覆盖 Madewell 40% 的产品线。<br></p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/fragrance/alexander-mcqueen-creates-fragrance-figure-eight-1202767944/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alexander McQueen 推出女士香水系列</a></strong>。<br></p><p>8 款香水均包含安息香、素心兰（檀香）和一款花香，容量为每瓶 75 毫升，定价 220 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801121200fRoTzvDPQq7sxm8M.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/345139/uniqlo-u-2018-qiudongxiliejijiangdengchang/\" rel=\"nofollow\">&nbsp;UNIQLO U 2018 秋冬系列即将发布</a></strong>。<br></p><p>首波单品将于 9 月 13 日在 UNIQLO 纽约第五大道旗舰店及官网发布，次日登陆其他指定零售商；第二波产品将于 10 月 11 日起开始发售。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801105525rbPMoYxjN3yDC2Zu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.141667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201808011055441MGhrCstWkwg9K80.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.435417\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801105558Sft3KxzrLanFOTMA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.435417\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801105614juDwgCsN385YQdXS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.435417\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201808011056189zIGjlWkJZKdfY6i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.435417\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801105625VG2IvODmBUrFQjq9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.435417\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801105635pGVQaj5DPouENx4H.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.435417\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801105645rwAWtqbcyF0OMTf8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.435417\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801105654QoHrAwWz2fs0CceV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.435417\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801105701l17jrixmeYLqaudB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.435417\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801105708mchMFlUqaGJpPtV7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.435417\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201808011057181EiuKtxmwJM4g9r7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.435417\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801105731vIglmuZ8NqLbfHk7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.435417\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801105743zeNVQBO71ERtihmH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.435417\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/wakino-japanese-armpit-ads-07-31-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本广告公司&nbsp;Wakino 正在招募愿意在腋窝上贴着广告到处走的年轻女模特</a></strong>。</p><p>Wakino 的母公司 Liberta 是日本一家专营腋下美容产品的公司。Wakino 称，腋窝是打广告的“黄金地段”，每小时只要付 1 万日元（612 元人民币），它就会将客户的定制广告贴在年轻女模特的腋窝上，而模特会尽其所能让大家看到广告。目前他们已经接到了第一笔订单，客户是一家美容和皮肤管理连锁店 Seishin Biyo Clinic，该连锁店用腋窝广告来推销自己的无痛除腋毛手术。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801112826mXwfIUnijl8xLA9G.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201808011128136QbLtYjx4WGapKrn.png\" data-ratio=\"0.658151\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801112751kovHIscJ1zn3VAq0.png\" data-ratio=\"0.667075\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801112807at14cbEN6gR7YBJC.png\" data-ratio=\"0.668299\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.wallpaper.com/fashion/martial-arts-gentle-monster-opens-a-kung-fu-inspired-london-boutique\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gentle Monster 欧洲首家旗舰店在伦敦 Argyll Street 28 - 29 号开业</a></strong>。</p><p>新店共两层，店铺设计围绕“外星武士”的主题。空间内随处可见穿着彩色盔甲、举起细长手臂高呼的“外星武士”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801113822RXMU4NqwHuczd5j2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.613043\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801113834dO93m2cAPjLsGBg1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.613043\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801113848MWN3ozAut8mI1KfP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.613043\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801113854IaAvWmDgflXoM7u0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.613043\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801113903kZJoCMjHsveR7FrV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.613043\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>有传言称，<strong><a href=\"http://www.dazeddigital.com/fashion/article/40839/1/tyler-mitchell-beyonce-vogue-us-cover-anna-wintour-first-black-photographer\" rel=\"nofollow\">23 岁的 Tyler Mitchell 将成为美国版《Vogue》126 年历史上首位拍摄 9 月刊封面的黑人摄影师</a></strong>。拍摄对象是&nbsp;Beyoncé。<br></p><p>Tyler Mitchell 去年刚从纽约大学毕业，随后集结自己花 6 周时间在古巴拍摄的纪实摄影，自费出版了一本 108 页的摄影集 <em>El Paquete。</em>这本摄影集引起了<em>《纽约时报》、《i-D 杂志》</em>等媒体的注意。目前 Tyler Mitchell 在 instagram 已有 7 万粉丝，其中包括&nbsp;Solange、Naomi Campbell 和 Rose McGowan 等人。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801115750mQlanYfwOSdzVLWE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.854962\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Tyler Mitchell&nbsp;</figcaption> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801115853oWTF0x5QSyleEj4b.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.728125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption><em>《El Paquete》</em></figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801115910GSP72DTAmsMUFgnk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.655469\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801115919H6CisvjfSA2uYUNx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.728125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801115925Pe4pujWab3qALohG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.728125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801115930qct27SuD9NsZgCTW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.655469\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801115936WbhAfRl7Puq1Lr4g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.728125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801115943kXHgUelmi5ZQKfMJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.728125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801120001hOPTD31m8aGy045V.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.728125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018080112001374s5lgRQLtraTb1M.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.728125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801120020sE0mvypz7fTYQLrG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.663281\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801120031Cn8MWjld7aHs0BJp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801120048fobFOD29UsQNqndu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.663281\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801120057ncT4wMHQFstj86Lu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.663281\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801120103E8bRNM2VoDqPWuF4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.663281\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801120114bKIrNByeQZ9v8mtW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.663281\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801120124ao1lbXF78BEkzxpi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801120132b5NjuStAlFiyCfVw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.507813\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201808011201388ms5TShF96KbfiZI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>临近七夕情人节，奢侈品牌又开始接连发布七夕限量款，宣传广告都拍得“十分接地气”。</strong></p><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.chinasspp.com/News/Detail/2018-7-31/421303.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">7 月 30 日，DIORAMOUR 系列中国独家限量版手袋在 Dior 七夕线上限时精品店发售，定价 34500 元</a></strong>。与往年的明星造势策略一样，Dior 今年邀请 Angelababy、王丽坤、景甜、孙伊涵和王子文为这一系列手袋拍摄了广告视频。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801124301PdcsRv1LJHiuOqBr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.452880\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801124317mHjwLsEWyvz0SRdN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.452880\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801124324FVpeKNDhuCZXrgtv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.456693\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801124331QDJotHUVMpdyne1C.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.347087\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.michaelkors.cn/trend/2018qixi_mkxym_video?utm_source=baidu&amp;utm_campaign=AUG&amp;utm_adgroup=BS35&amp;utm_medium=brandzone&amp;utm_content=banner\" rel=\"nofollow\">Michael Kors 与品牌全球代言人杨幂合作推出特别款 Whitney 手袋</a></strong>。手袋共有红黑两色，定价 5900 元，同样于品牌微信小程序上线，并将于 8 月 1 日至 19 日以及 8 月 25 日至 9 月 2 日分别在上海静安嘉里中心和成都太古里展出。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801124550JLRwBhFlq1vpdbKf.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.952778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.chinasspp.com/News/Detail/2018-7-31/421302.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">Givenchy 今年没有再和包先生或 Gogoboi 等博主合作</a></strong>，推出的 2018 年七夕红色特别款 GV3 手袋将于 8 月 5 日上午 10 点在品牌微信小程序上出售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801124736NhBs9YZKTHdw4XUF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.406667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1607117390107297875&amp;wfr=spider&amp;for=pc\" rel=\"nofollow\">历峰集团旗下品牌万宝龙（Montblanc）与博主包先生合作</a></strong>，于 7 月 26 日在包先生的微信小程序“包铺BAOSHOP”上发售了 497 只联名手袋，其中包括男女黑色双肩包各 199 只以及 99 只粉色女士双肩包，据称“36 小时全部售罄”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801124858VdX9krxAg5cJyp0P.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.511811\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801124838tboXsq9dHlfEc7Ap.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.181818\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图为<strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/wakino-japanese-armpit-ads-07-31-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Wakino</a>&nbsp;腋窝广告</strong></p>"}